<div class="jumbotron">
        <h1 class="display-3">Play Time Calculator</h1>
        <p class="lead">This is a simple calcuation for figuring out how much earned time the child must log in order to gain a specific amount of play time!</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
<form>
How many minutes of play time would your child like to earn? <input class="form-control" type="number" id="firstNumber" /><br>
At what percentage is the child's productive task weighted? <input class="form-control" type="number" id="secondNumber" placeholder="Ex: If 90%, enter .90" /><br>
<button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onClick="divideBy()">Calculate</button>
</form>
<br>
<p>The approximate amount of productive time (in minutes) you must log: <strong><span id = "result"></span></strong></p>